quran[26{c,v,t}:
69,9,Wa jaaa'a Firawnu wa man qablahoo wal mu'tafikaatu bilhaati'ah
69,10,Fa'ansaw Rasoola Rabbihim fa akhazahum akhzatar raabiyah
69,11,Innaa lammaa taghal maaa'u hamalnaakum fil jaariyah
69,12,Linaj'alahaa lakum tazki ratanw-wa ta'iyahaa unzununw waa'iyah
69,13,Fa izaa nufikha fis soori nafkhatunw waahidah
69,14,Wa humilatil ardu wal jibaalu fadukkataa dakkatanw waahidah
69,15,Fa yawma'izinw waqa'atil waaqi'ah
69,16,Wanshaqqatis samaaa'u fahiya yawma 'izinw-waahiyah
69,17,Wal malaku 'alaaa arjaaa'ihaa; wa yahmilu 'Arsha Rabbika fawqahum yawma'izin samaaniyah
69,18,Yawma'izin tu'radoona laa takhfaa min kum khaafiyah
69,19,Fa ammaa man ootiya kitaabahoo biyameenihee fa yaqoolu haaa'umuq ra'oo kitaabiyah
69,20,Innee zannantu annee mulaaqin hisaabiyah
69,21,Fahuwa fee 'eeshatir raadiyah
69,22,Fee jannnatin 'aaliyah
69,23,Qutoofuhaa daaniyah
69,24,Kuloo washraboo haneee'am bimaaa aslaftum fil ayyaamil khaliyah
69,25,Wa ammaa man ootiya kitaabahoo bishimaalihee fa yaqoolu yaalaitanee lam oota kitaaabiyah
69,26,Wa lam adri maa hisaabiyah
69,27,Yaa laitahaa kaanatil qaadiyah
69,28,Maaa aghnaa 'annee maaliyah
69,29,Halaka 'annee sultaaniyah
69,30,Khuzoohu faghullooh
69,31,Summal Jaheema sallooh
69,32,Summa fee silsilatin zar'uhaa sab'oona ziraa'an faslukooh
69,33,Innahoo kaana laa yu'minubillaahil 'Azeem
69,34,wa laa yahuddu 'alaa ta'aamil miskeen
